title: Hospitable England in the seventies;
author: Dana, Richard Henry
snippet: After lunch went to a flower and vegetable show at Inchture got up by Lord and Lady Kinnaird.

title: Hospitable England in the seventies;
author: Dana, Richard Henry
snippet: Left Edinburgh for Inchture where I found Lord Kinnaird' s carriage waiting for me, and I drove to Rossie Priory by a very picturesque route.
